<p><strong>What I Can Give:</strong> Pretty much any sort of writing, though SCPs and Tales is where I feel more comfortable. Although I'm comfortable with most topic and themes, I would be most grateful if the requested piece of writing wasn't associated with any canon or The Fifth Church, since I'm not that informed about them or confident enough to write for a group of interest I haven't really explored. Preferably, I would also like to not have to do a million articles of background reading (obviously I’m fine with having to read <em>some</em> background stuff, since it’s obvious I would have to do so, just not a lot, please).</p>
<p><strong>What I Am Looking For:</strong> Any article (tale, SCP, GoI format, whatever suits you fancy) involving <a href="/scp-5464">The Obearwatch Command</a> (everything about as it currently stands in explained in the linked article).</p>
<div class="collapsible-block">
<div class="collapsible-block-folded"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">+&nbsp;Some&nbsp;additional&nbsp;minor&nbsp;rules&nbsp;I&nbsp;have&nbsp;in&nbsp;mind&nbsp;for&nbsp;the&nbsp;group</a></div>
