<div class="collapsible-block-content">
<ul>
<li>Think of the group as an archon-bear-related-dado-ish-Department of Abnormalities-esque bunch. Though not much is really known about the group itself they somehow keep appearing in the weirdest of places; it's not really even known if the name 'Obearwatch Command' is the group itself or merely the name of the group ruling it. Are people behind it people or bears? No one truly knows!</li>
<li>Though most of the time their actions seem illogical, they always have a purpose to them, with 99% of the time ends up being beneficial to everyone.</li>
<li>The Foundation doesn't really try to stop the group in their actions since most of them do not harm anyone and don't risk the reveal of the supernatural (see - 5464).</li>
<li>All of their actions are in some way bear-related.</li>
</ul>
</div>
